Changes to 0.2:
---------------
-more behind-the-scenes use of QT built-ins
-now by default does an initial save/load to make sure the hardware controls are set to the same values reported by alsa

Changes to 0.16:
----------------
-added callback loop that updates controls when modified by other programs
-added support for arbitrary alsa devices

Changes between 0.1 and 0.14:
-----------------------------
-added save/load functionality
-added command line interface
-fixed minor UI issues
-changed some functionality behind the scenes
